description:
BLiPSDKHelper helps build Resources on BlipSDK C# in a simpler way: 

Resources: 
- Text 
- Images 
- Videos 
- Web Link 
- Menu 
- List 
- QuickReply 
- Carousel 
- MultipleDocuments 
- Receipt
- CallButton

- Updates

 - One service for each messaging channel (Facebook Messenger and BlipChat Channel).
 - Better way to build objects and better way to know what element is supported by each channel.
